  <!-- @import "site-sidebar.kit" -->

  <p>For consistency throughout Codebase, some <code>$deco-</code> variables have been defined. Where necessary, a few of these variables have been used in the various utilities and components.</p>
  
  <p>These same variables have been incoporated into a set of simple <code>.deco-</code> decoration classes. These classes can be used to quickly add consistent styling to your HTML directly.</p>
  
  <p>You can modify these <code>$deco*</code> variables and <code>.deco-</code> classes, and add to them, in accordance with the style guide or visual identity of your website project.</p>

